{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4024_00_01","textHome":"我是米诺……为了实现母亲大人的愿望，现在@正在帮忙参与一场战争。眼下烦恼的是，法@兰西的乡村中出现了一位被称为「圣女」的@魔法少女。如果不是她的话，现在法兰西已@经落入我们的手中了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":402400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":402400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":402400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":402400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":402400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":402400}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":402400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4024_00_17","textHome":"被国王所抛弃，继续着无谓的抵抗的身姿。挺@身而出帮助同伴的身姿……演员们美丽而又@愚蠢的样子，才是悲剧最棒的调味品。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":402400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":402400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402400}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":402400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4024_00_18","textHome":"我有着很多想做成的事……要是说最想做的事@的话，答案就是和那个人永远在一起。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":402400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":402400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":402400,"motion":1}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4024_00_19","textHome":"这样，就能让舞台更加华丽了吧。"}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402400,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4024_00_20","textHome":"哼哼……当一时的主角似乎也不错呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":402400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402400}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4024_00_21","textHome":"我的愿望，是献给伟大的母亲大人的。所以，@这得到的崭新力量，我也会为了母亲大人而@使用。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":402400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":402400,"motion":300}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4024_00_22","textHome":"哎呀，我本来并不打算自己能够强到这种地步@的……支配这个国家，为母亲的梦想……尽@一份绵薄之力的同时，就让更戏剧的演出能@够上演吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":402400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":402400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402400,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4024_00_23","textHome":"如果管看到之前看不到的东西叫做“成长”的@话，那我现在就是这种状态。哼哼……为了@法兰西存亡而战斗的人做着无谓的努力，看@起来是多么愚蠢，多么的卑微……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":402400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":402400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402400}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402451,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4024_51_24"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":402451}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402451,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.